dcterms:description: The QM9 dataset contains predicted atomization energies and uncertainties, reference values, and molecular formulas as input features. It is used to evaluate the performance of the BVS method in improving consistency and adaptivity in uncertainty quantification.
dcterms:title: QM9 dataset

dcterms:description: The OxNy group dataset is used to evaluate the performance of the BVS method based on the oxygen and nitrogen content of molecular groups. It aims to improve adaptivity in uncertainty quantification.
dcterms:title: OxNy group dataset
